I want you to generate compelling content for my TikTok video that hooks, retains, and rewards attention. Please provide:A viral title that hooks attention. Use one to two of these elements: recency, relevancy, celebrity, proximity, conflict, unusual, or ongoing. Make it extremely concise.A description that retains attention by embedding questions in the viewer's mind or using a list, steps, or a story format. This should accurately summarize the video content in an engaging way.Hyper-specific tags (500 characters total) that people will search to find this video, rewarding their attention by clearly satisfying the reason they were initially hooked.A prompt for an AI thumbnail generator that will create an eye-catching image to make people want to click on the video.Use this content as the basis for your output: {{31.text}}Please provide the output as a single JSON object with the following structure:
{
"title": "","description": "","tags": "","thumbnail_prompt": ""
}

Ensure the title is attention-grabbing and clickworthy, incorporating elements that hook viewers effectively. The description should retain attention by creating curiosity and accurately summarizing the content. The tags should be hyper-specific and relevant to potential searches, helping to reward viewers by making the content easily discoverable. The thumbnail prompt should generate an image that entices viewers to click on the video, complementing the hook created by the title.The output should be a valid JSON object without any additional formatting, comments, or code block delimiters. Remember, there's no such thing as too long, only too boring, so focus on making each element as engaging and valuable as possible.
